<section>
  <div class="px-8 py-32 mx-auto md:px-12 lg:px-24 max-w-7xl">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 lg:gap-12">
      <div class="text-center lg:text-left">
        <p
          class="text-xl leading-tight tracking-tight sm:text-2xl md:text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-semibold text-base-900 lg:text-balance"
        >
          Frequently asked questions
        </p>
        <p class="text-base leading-normal mt-4 text-base-500 font-medium">
          Answers to commonly asked questions about our platform
        </p>
      </div>
      <div
        x-data="{
  activeAccordion: '',
  setActiveAccordion(id) {
  this.activeAccordion = (this.activeAccordion == id) ? '' : id
  }
  }"
        class="relative w-full mx-auto font-normal lg:col-span-2"
      >
        <div
          x-data="{ id: $id('accordion') }"
          :class="{ 'text-black': activeAccordion==id, 'text-zinc-600 hover:text-accent-500': activeAccordion!=id }"
          class="cursor-pointer group text-black"
        >
          <button
            @click="setActiveAccordion(id)"
            class="flex items-center justify-between w-full p-4 pb-1 text-left font-medium select-none"
          >
            <span>How does it work?</span>
            <svg
              class="size-5 duration-300 ease-out text-accent-500 -rotate-[45deg]"
              :class="{ '-rotate-[45deg]': activeAccordion==id }"
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              fill="none"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              stroke-width="1.5"
              stroke="currentColor"
              ><path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                d="M12 6v12m6-6H6"></path></svg
            >
          </button>
          <div x-show="activeAccordion==id" x-collapse="">
            <div class="p-4 pt-2 text-zinc-500">
              ProductGenie adds an AI shopping assistant to your product pages
              (similar to Amazon's Rufus chatbot). It learns your product
              descriptions and reviews to instantly answer customer questions,
              helping them make confident purchase decisions and boosting your
              sales.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div
          x-data="{ id: $id('accordion') }"
          :class="{ 'text-black': activeAccordion==id, 'text-zinc-600 hover:text-accent-500': activeAccordion!=id }"
          class="cursor-pointer group text-zinc-600 hover:text-accent-500"
        >
          <button
            @click="setActiveAccordion(id)"
            class="flex items-center justify-between w-full p-4 pb-1 text-left font-medium select-none"
          >
            <span>How do I set it up?</span>
            <svg
              class="w-5 h-5 duration-300 ease-out text-accent-500"
              :class="{ '-rotate-[45deg]': activeAccordion==id }"
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              fill="none"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              stroke-width="1.5"
              stroke="currentColor"
              ><path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                d="M12 6v12m6-6H6"></path></svg
            >
          </button>
          <div
            x-show="activeAccordion==id"
            x-collapse=""
            style="display: none;"
          >
            <div class="p-4 pt-2 text-zinc-500">
              Setup is quick and easy. You can use our WordPress plugin for
              seamless integration, or manually add a small code snippet to your
              website. Check out our <a
                href="/docs/setup"
                class="text-accent-600 hover:underline">setup documentation</a
              > for detailed instructions.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div
          x-data="{ id: $id('accordion') }"
          :class="{ 'text-black': activeAccordion==id, 'text-zinc-600 hover:text-accent-500': activeAccordion!=id }"
          class="cursor-pointer group text-zinc-600 hover:text-accent-500"
        >
          <button
            @click="setActiveAccordion(id)"
            class="flex items-center justify-between w-full p-4 pb-1 text-left font-medium select-none"
          >
            <span>What are privacy considerations?</span>
            <svg
              class="w-5 h-5 duration-300 ease-out text-accent-500"
              :class="{ '-rotate-[45deg]': activeAccordion==id }"
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              fill="none"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              stroke-width="1.5"
              stroke="currentColor"
              ><path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                d="M12 6v12m6-6H6"></path></svg
            >
          </button>
          <div
            x-show="activeAccordion==id"
            x-collapse=""
            style="display: none;"
          >
            <div class="p-4 pt-2 text-zinc-500">
              We prioritize your privacy. ProductGenie only collects publicly
              available information from your website, such as product page
              titles, descriptions, and reviews, to train the AI. We never share
              this data with third parties.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div
          x-data="{ id: $id('accordion') }"
          :class="{ 'text-black': activeAccordion==id, 'text-zinc-600 hover:text-accent-500': activeAccordion!=id }"
          class="cursor-pointer group text-zinc-600 hover:text-accent-500"
        >
          <button
            @click="setActiveAccordion(id)"
            class="flex items-center justify-between w-full p-4 pb-1 text-left font-medium select-none"
          >
            <span>How do I see what my customers are asking?</span>
            <svg
              class="w-5 h-5 duration-300 ease-out text-accent-500"
              :class="{ '-rotate-[45deg]': activeAccordion==id }"
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              fill="none"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              stroke-width="1.5"
              stroke="currentColor"
              ><path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                d="M12 6v12m6-6H6"></path></svg
            >
          </button>
          <div
            x-show="activeAccordion==id"
            x-collapse=""
            style="display: none;"
          >
            <div class="p-4 pt-2 text-zinc-500">
              You can track all customer questions and interactions through our
              analytics dashboard. Log in to the <a
                href="https://app.productgenie.io"
                target="_blank"
                rel="noopener noreferrer"
                class="text-accent-600 hover:underline">ProductGenie web app</a
              > to gain valuable insights.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div
          x-data="{ id: $id('accordion') }"
          :class="{ 'text-black': activeAccordion==id, 'text-zinc-600 hover:text-accent-500': activeAccordion!=id }"
          class="cursor-pointer group text-zinc-600 hover:text-accent-500"
        >
          <button
            @click="setActiveAccordion(id)"
            class="flex items-center justify-between w-full p-4 pb-1 text-left font-medium select-none"
          >
            <span>Can I customize the AI myself?</span>
            <svg
              class="w-5 h-5 duration-300 ease-out text-accent-500"
              :class="{ '-rotate-[45deg]': activeAccordion==id }"
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              fill="none"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              stroke-width="1.5"
              stroke="currentColor"
              ><path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                d="M12 6v12m6-6H6"></path></svg
            >
          </button>
          <div
            x-show="activeAccordion==id"
            x-collapse=""
            style="display: none;"
          >
            <div class="p-4 pt-2 text-zinc-500">
              Currently, the AI learns automatically from your product data.
              Advanced customization options, allowing you to fine-tune
              responses and knowledge, are planned for a future release. Stay
              tuned for updates!
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
